item.title: About Me
item.description: Howdy! I’m Miguel! I’m a student at Plano East Senior High School studying computer science. I’ve always been interested in how technology shapes our daily lives from a very young age, which led me to pursue a career where I could explore and learn new things. My Journey I was born and raised in Dallas, Texas. From the day I was born, I was fascinated by anything with an on-and-off switch.
